content.body:
### Shop P195/60R16 Tire Size 
The P195/60R16 tire size is one you’ll find on the Audi A4, Chrysler PT Cruiser, and Volkswagen Golf. If you’re driving something that is rolling on P195/60R16 tires, you are probably looking for all-season tires that offer predictable handling, a comfortable ride, good road manners, and year-round traction on wet or dry pavement. Or, perhaps you like to really get the most out of your vehicle’s handling and cornering potential with ultra-high-performance and summer tires. Just remember that UHP tires use a softer, “stickier'' tread formulation that stiffens in colder weather, and shouldn’t be used when it’s colder than about 45 degrees Fahrenheit outside.

Looking for a new set of P195/60R16 tires? Take a look at the Michelin Premier A/S, [Yokohama Avid Ascend LX](https://simpletire.com/brands/yokohama-tires/avid-ascend-lx), and Hankook Kinergy GT (H436) if you need a set of tires that are engineered to perform year-round. 

Maybe you want something sporty. If that’s the case, consider the [Kumho Ecsta PA31](https://simpletire.com/brands/kumho-tires/ecsta-pa31) and Dunlop SP Sport 5000; just remember to swap them for all-season or winter tires once temperatures are consistently below 45 degrees Fahrenheit.

Whether you need an all-season, ultra-high-performance, or another type of tire, SimpleTire has a set of P195/60R16 tires that meets your needs at a great price!
